OL,3,CCouncils warn SEND deficits mean they
OL,4,Ccould go bankrupt 'overnight'
OL,6,FA decision to let English councils
OL,7,Fbuild up "hidden deficits" to cover
OL,8,Fthe surging cost of special
OL,9,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,10,F(SEND) now risks bankrupting almost
OL,11,Fthree-quarters of the largest local
OL,12,Fauthorities, it has been warned.
OL,14,FResearch shared exclusively with ITV
OL,15,FNews and the FT reveals that councils
OL,16,F- which have been allowed to use an
OL,17,Faccounting fudge to keep the losses
OL,18,Foff their balance sheets - have
OL,19,Falready amassed SEND deficits of #4
OL,20,Fbillion nationwide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
