OL,6,FThe number of children with an EHCP
OL,7,F(Education Health and Care Plan) that
OL,8,Fcarries statutory support has risen
OL,9,Ffrom 240,183 to 575,973 since 2014.
OL,10,FAnother 1.2 million children fall
OL,11,Fbelow that threshold but still qualify
OL,12,Ffor extra care. Many more children are
OL,13,Fnow schooled in special schools,
OL,14,Fincluding private options paid for by
OL,15,Flocal authorities.
